    "# Personal Fitness Recommender - Training Notebook\n",
    "\n",
    "## Overview\n",
    "This notebook trains a PyTorch neural network to recommend workout types (cardio, strength, mixed, rest_light) based on user inputs: age, weight, height, fitness goal, and activity level.\n",
    "\n",
    "## Steps\n",
    "1. Generate synthetic dataset\n",
    "2. Preprocess data (encode, scale)\n",
    "3. Build and train the model\n",
    "4. Evaluate performance\n",
    "5. Save model and preprocessors\n",
    "\n",
    "## Requirements\n",
    "- PyTorch\n",
    "- Scikit-learn\n",
    "- Pandas, NumPy\n",
    "\n",
    "Run cells in order for a complete training pipeline."
   ]
  },
